{
  "stem": "21786.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For he died in 1940, when we couldn't go back and forth to visit him anymore for there was a curfew for Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was buried in the place where I knew my great-grandfather was born, very close to the place where he lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The place is a village, which we visited about three weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, I have to spell the name, K-R-A-S-O-N-O-V-I-C-E, Krasonovice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was buried in something which is called-- where was a small Jewish cemetery in Z-B-R-A-S-L-A-V-I-C-E, Zbraslavice where there was also a small temple shul, which was destroyed, which became, I think, a school.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the small cemetery in Zbraslavice, I couldn't find.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This year, I found it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I found also that the Czechs were not so bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They left the tombstone standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somebody took care of the grass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only, somehow, the wall disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There are, more or less, summer cottages around it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "For there is-- it's on a hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And underneath, there's a brook or a little river.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I found there are 16 Spitz's 16 graves, tombs of various Spitz's.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It must have been a kind of endemic name in that region.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- with the years, I taught myself that I was closer to my maternal grandfather.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think it just caused by the fact that, at that point, I didn't forgive my father for my sister.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure I was closer to my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once Hitler marched in, so the company was dissolved practically within a few months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was quite a resourceful man, but he became pretty desolate and defeated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the whole family, family life, and family clan, which was around was disrupted by this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was obvious that he should have left.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
